      <title>英国消费者对“双底萎缩通胀”有所警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/british-shoppers-wise-up-to-double-dip-shrinkflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国消费者注意到了“双底缩水通胀”，由于供应商试图保护其利润，巧克力和薯片等产品的体积缩小了数倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/british-shoppers-wise-up-to-double-dip-shrinkflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
